PM2 Command to run node app in the background:

1. Command to list all documnets: pm2 list: 
2. Command to start pm2 application: pm2 start npm --name "AppName" -- start
3. Command to stop application: pm2 stop "AppName"
4. Commnad to delete application: pm2 delete "AppName"

Nohup command to run python app in background:
-nohup python run-dev.py &> cloudspin_log.out&

